00:00:33.460 --> 00:00:40.460
creates this field within you and is in the
Gita. Shri Krishna has talked about the field

00:00:43.190 --> 00:00:50.190
that we all have a Pradesh - is the field
but Desh means the field and the enlightened

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:59.480
one is the Pradesh. And that same thing happens
to us when this Kundalini rises within you.

