Holy Ghost and we didn’t give Christ much

00:01:17.180 --> 00:01:23.600
chance to speak about it. He could only speak
for three and a half years, is nothing. I

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:30.600
can tell you three and a half years in this
land anywhere in the whole world it’s so

00:01:32.580 --> 00:01:39.580
difficult even to convince four people that
they have to seek the truth, it’s very difficult.

